 Julian Rachlin will replace violinist Midori in the Oct. 23 concert by 
Esa-Pekka Salonen and the Los Angeles Philharmonic sponsored by the Orange 
County Philharmonic Society at the Orange County Performing Arts Center in 
Costa Mesa.Midori has canceled her entire fall tour schedule because of 
