<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA092694-0110 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 082938 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 26, 1994, Monday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 2; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1099 words 
