<P>
 Service to Provide Market Analyses in Chinese: Dow Jones Telerate, which 
provides financial information on computer screens, said it has teamed up with 
AIM Y.K. Hui Investment Consultants Ltd. of Hong Kong to provide analysis of 
financial markets in Chinese.The service, which will begin in November, will 
initially cover foreign exchange, precious metals, stock and base metals 
markets. Telerate, a wholly owned unit of Dow Jones & Co. Inc., plans to add 
analysis of individual companies next year. The company already provides 
financial information in Chinese to subscribers in 80 cities in China. 
